ENCAPSULATION: -wrapping up the data and methods to the class that manipulates them.
               -used to make sure that the private data remains hidden from user.
                For modification or to read one can use get method and set method.
                BENEFITS:You (or others) can change one part of the code without
                          affecting other parts
                          Increased security of data

Get:get are public functions used to get private data members in the
        class.
        string get_private-member-name()
        {
            return name;
        }
Set:Set are public functions used to set private data members in the class.
        void set_private-member-name(pass parameter)
        {
             name=parameter;
        }
        